<h2 id="orgheadline2">Update <span class="timestamp-wrapper"><span class="timestamp">04 Mar 2016</span></span></h2>
<div class="outline-text-2" id="text-orgheadline2">
<p>
Fixed a function call to the new name.</p>
</div>
